text: Meguid (), extended form Abdel Meguid (), is an Egyptian surname. Notable people with this surname include: * Abdel Meguid Amir (born 1961), Egyptian basketball player * Abdel Meguid Mahmoud (born 1946), Egyptian politician * Ahmed Abdel-Meguid, (1923-2013), Egyptian diplomat * Ibrahim Abdel Meguid, Egyptian author * Michael M. Meguid, Egyptian-American surgeon * Nagwa Abdel Meguid, Egyptian geneticist * Omar Abdel Meguid (born 1988), Egyptian squash player * Wahid Abdel Meguid, Egyptian politician
title: Meguid
